{"tid":818440,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[又嚟]大摩：濠賭股目前周期與2012年初相似 若重現股價或彈50%","createTime":"2018-09-14T06:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T11:10:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb491ef4c65b10c688074b050e572f63aff2095","tid":818440,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"摩根士丹利發表報告表示，澳門博彩行業目前放緩趨勢與2011/2012年相似，即中場表現仍然鞏固，但貴賓廳收入由原來增長65%，調整至倒跌8%，倘若今輪濠賭股股價走勢周期，與上一次周期(2012年1月至4月)呈現重覆，按周期走勢估算，濠賭股今輪周期此階段股價或反彈50%。<br />\n<br />\n該行解釋，若今輪濠賭股股價走勢周期，與上一次周期(2012年1月至4月)呈現重覆，即濠賭股股價走勢會經歷三個階段，第一個階段是股價先調整30%(上輪周期此階段為2011年7月至2012年1月)(對比今輪周期此階段為2018年年4月至9月)，第二階段是反彈50%(上輪周期此階段為2012年1月至4月)，第三階段股價再回落30%(上輪周期此階段為2012年4月底至7月底)。<br />\n<br />\n該行指，基於濠賭股上一輪周期在博彩收入增長緩下，主要受貴賓廳收入由原來增長65%調整至倒跌8%(在2011/2012年期間)(對比2017/2018年由增長37%放緩至1%)，雖然盈利預測下調，但中場仍然鞏固，行業EBITDA增長令人意外，刺激濠賭股於上一輪周期第二個階段股價反彈50%。<br />\n<br />\n大摩表示，濠賭股於上一輪周期第二個階段(即2012年1月至4月)，濠賭股EBITDA按季升48%、按年升52%令市場驚喜，因中場表現穩固，刺激濠賭股在此階段股價累積反彈50%。而該行估計澳門博彩行業2018年第三季EBITDA按年升19%(按季升9%)，濠賭股將於10月及11月公布第三季EBITDA表現，料可推動股價回升。<br />\n<br />\n但該行亦指出，濠賭股於上一輪周期第三個階段(即2012年4月至7月)，再經歷行業EBITDA增長放緩，令市場下調對相關股份估值預測，觸發相關股份期內股價再回調30%。(wl/u)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00027/NOW.897036/all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fanalysis%2Fstock-aafn-content%2F00027%2FNOW.897036%2Fall&d=prQzaSRThAvUF1LR3lMCpMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3bb52bab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/analysis/stock-aafn-content/00027/NOW.897036/all</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e971fa55d99f60467ccf5be94cbe0623d7935f","tid":818440,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"投行要出貨啦快撚D入市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606f5cd27bdd02c78eabae63a61ea02225f5c09c","tid":818440,"uid":91982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c948a214bfe34b957ab0a53cfbeb0f0fa5a0f55","tid":818440,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:13:51.000Z","msg":"返去跑馬啦大摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91913b8a94228f6dfc6936e754b6f3c85526144","tid":818440,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"想出貨呀大摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8080193bfac37cd1319390eaabd8a97485c93316","tid":818440,"uid":1462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"仲有人信投行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n08炒到大大獲<br />\n獲獲9up想出貨<br />\n入貨正傻仔"},{"pid":"1ebb117e9ccbaae980a77254d712a0111ddbbf13","tid":818440,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"屌啲理由可唔可以唔好咁鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b91e60c4c6f0770796c54b57773a8724f04c09","tid":818440,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"係會同2012相似。個股價呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81754bafc23a670460385497cd222b29b82acc1","tid":818440,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"彈佢老母個閪喇<br />\n隻200由1年高位跌左1半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb77b07ab526cfaef8c1236747288c353bb877d","tid":818440,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:45:07.00